# ROCm/HIP root-level inventory

upstream_repo: ROCm/hip
upstream_url: https://github.com/ROCm/hip
source_view: GitHub mobile file browser screenshots + prior upstream metadata
created_for: Netiv ROCN research library
scope: first-level folders and root files only
status: manual root-level inventory

FORMAT:
path | kind | apparent purpose

================================================================================
FIRST-LEVEL FOLDERS
================================================================================
.azuredevops/ | folder | Azure DevOps CI configuration.
.github/ | folder | GitHub repository metadata and workflow automation.
.jenkins/ | folder | Jenkins CI support files.
bin/ | folder | HIP command/tool helper scripts.
cmake/ | folder | CMake integration and FindHIP/build support.
docker/ | folder | Docker/container build or test support.
docs/ | folder | HIP documentation source.
include/ | folder | Public HIP include headers.

================================================================================
ROOT FILES
================================================================================
.clang-format | config | Clang-format source formatting rules.
.gitattributes | config | Git attributes for repository file handling.
.gitignore | config | Git ignore rules.
.markdownlint-cli2.yaml | config | Markdown linting configuration.
.readthedocs.yaml | config | ReadTheDocs documentation build configuration.
.spellcheck.local.yaml | config | Local spellcheck configuration.
.wordlist.txt | text/config | Custom accepted word list for documentation/spellcheck.
CODEOWNERS | repo metadata | GitHub code owner routing/review metadata.
CONTRIBUTING.md | documentation | Contribution rules and process notes.
Jenkinsfile | CI config | Root Jenkins pipeline entry.
LICENSE.md | legal | HIP repository license file.
README-doc.md | documentation | Detailed HIP project documentation README.
README.md | documentation | Short HIP repository overview.
VERSION | metadata | Version marker file.
configure | script | Configure helper script.
hip-lang-config.cmake.in | build config | CMake HIP language configuration template.
install.sh | script | Install helper script.

================================================================================
ROCN NOTES
================================================================================
This file intentionally stops at the first level of the upstream ROCm/HIP repo.
Do not treat this as a complete recursive manifest.

Next staged scans can go folder-by-folder:

1. .github/
2. bin/
3. cmake/
4. docs/
5. include/
6. docker/
7. .azuredevops/
8. .jenkins/
